Product Description▼▲
Joined by the African Children's Choir and Israel Houghton, Smitty elevates live worship to a new level! Includes familiar favorites "Mighty to Save" and "Majesty" as well as "Help Is on the Way" (with Houghton), "Shout unto God," "Prepare Ye the Way," "Draw Me Near," "The River Is Rising," and the title track with the Children's Choir.

